title: Ahmed Fathi Hammadi
text:
Ahmed Fathi (born 24 August 1949) was a former <a href="Iraq">Iraq</a>i <a href="association%20football">football</a> <a href="Forward%20%28association%20football%29">forward</a> who played for <a href="Iraq%20national%20football%20team">Iraq</a> in the <a href="1972%20AFC%20Asian%20Cup">1972 AFC Asian Cup</a>.
He played for the national team between 1972 and 1973.
